name: Decentral Games ICE Poker
description:
Step into the ICE Poker Arcade and play in poker tournaments to win big prizes like MacBooks, iPhones, and more. Join thousands of players worldwide on the first Metaverse poker platform.

ICE Poker dress code: you need to equip a wearable to play. Owning an All Access wearable unlocks all game modes and platforms for the full ICE Poker experience.

To learn more about ICE Poker, visit: https://decentral.games/
